ate (\"ASU\") No. 2015-03 (Subtopic 835-30) - Simplifying the", "bbox": [131.3, 410.0, 1157.3, 430.7]}, {"text": "Presentation of Debt Issuance Costs, requiring that debt issuance costs related to a recognized debt liability be presented in the balance", "bbox": [131.3, 428.7, 1157.3, 449.5]}, {"text": "sheet as a direct deduction from the carrying amount of that debt liability, consistent with debt discounts. Other long-term assets and long-", "bbox": [131.3, 447.5, 1152.5, 468.3]}, {"text": "term debt in the prior years were retrospectively adjusted to conform to the required presentation.", "bbox": [131.3, 466.3, 866.8, 487.0]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [84.4, 490.7, 106.4, 514.1]}, {"text": "Fiscal 2017 includes an estimated $394.0 million recorded in long-term income taxes payable related to the one-time transition tax as a", "bbox": [131.3, 493.3, 1157.2, 514.1]}, {"text": "result of the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act.", "bbox": [131.3, 512.1, 402.1, 532.9]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [84.4, 536.5, 108.0, 560.0]}, {"text": "Fiscal year 2017 includes the adoption of ASU No. 2016-09 (Topic 718) Compensation—Stock Compensation: Improvements to Employee", "bbox": [131.3, 539.2, 1157.2, 560.0]}, {"text": "Share-Based Payment Accounting, which simplifies several aspects of the accounting for share-based payment transactions, including the", "bbox": [131.3, 557.9, 1157.2, 578.7]}, {"text": "accounting for forfeitures, among other things. The Company elected to account for forfeitures as they occur using a modified retrospective", "bbox": [131.3, 576.7, 1157.2, 597.5]}, {"text": "transition method, rather than estimating forfeitures, resulting in a cumulative-effect adjustment of $9.0 million, which increased the", "bbox": [131.3, 595.5, 1157.3, 616.2]}, {"text": "January 1, 2017 opening accumulated deficit balance on the Consolidated Balance Sheets.", "bbox": [131.3, 614.2, 807.9, 635.0]}]}